                            <h5 class="mt-0 mb-1">Frequent Medical check-up</h5>
                            <p class="pera-bottom mb-30">    Frequent medical check-ups for those who are always exposed to hazardous substances or chemicals will help to identify the diseases at the initial stage itself and can be easily able to protect oneself. Workers should get flu-shots. </p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="media my-4">
                        <img src="~/Images/risk.svg" class="mr-3 img-thumbnail rounded-circle img-fluid" alt="...">
                        <div class="media-body">
